suncertify.model.db
Class DBFileContractorModel

java.lang.Object
  suncertify.model.db.DBFileContractorModel
All Implemented Interfaces:
ContractorModel
public class DBFileContractorModel
extends java.lang.Object
implements ContractorModel

An implementation for ContractorModel which converts string array records data retrieved from DBMain as Contractor instances and visa versa.

It needs a Session from which to have an access to a database file data through interface DBMain, an instance of it is retrieved by calling Session.getDataAccess() It depends on Schema to convert string array records to a contractor beans.

Author:
Mohammad S. Abdellatif
See Also:
ContractorModel, Contractor, Engine
